    <p class="ni">
      <strong>
	<font size="+2"> Dr. Alain Delgado Gran </font><br>
	&nbsp;<br>
      </strong>
        Advanced Research Complex ARC, Rm. 409 </br>
        25 Templeton Street, </br> 
        Ottawa, ON, Canada. <br />
        K1N6N5 </br>
        Tel. (613)-5625800 ext. 4884 <br />
        email: <a href="mailto:agran@uottawa.ca">agran@uottawa.ca</a>
    </p>

    <pbold>Areas of interest:</pbold><br />
      <ul>
         <li>Electronic structure calculations in condensed matter physics and quantum chemistry.</li>
         <li>Optical properties of semiconductor nanostructures and molecules in complex dielectric environments.</li>
         <li>Charge-transfer excitations in hybrid systems with photovoltaic/biological applications. </li>
         <li>Ultrafast (sub 100 fs) dynamics of photoexcited states in organic nanomaterials.</li>
         <li>Computational implementation of many-body methods for large-scale calculations in material science.</li>
      </ul>

    <pbold>Selected publications:</pbold><br />
